64
00:05:32.496 --> 00:05:34.646
Ty, telefonul.

65
00:05:43.726 --> 00:05:46.376
- Poate că e la duș.
- Nu.


66
00:05:46.376 --> 00:05:48.497
Squishy nu are un frate.

67
00:05:48.497 --> 00:05:49.806
